column1: Baby Barnaby's////Baby Barnaby's is a nice breakfast place that provides you with standard breakfast entrees. Pancakes
column4: you name it and they probably have it. I have to say though
column5: I do thoroughly enjoy their fruity pancakes (banana walnut in particular). I have also had their english muffins
column6: but it was kind of a sorry piece of toast looking thing (APPARENTLY ENGLISH MUFFIN ISNOT A MUFFIN... yeah i am not very 'cultured').
